title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps his time off. Which super popular singer did he hang out with? The Tampa Times' Rick Stroud calls in to discuss Tom Brady's hiatus. And Dan Orlovsky tells us why he's all in on the Broncos this season. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
